                  <join result="offencePlace" targOrder="Y" targets="t17860830-70-off352 t17860830-70-crimeloc355"></join>, I saw the prisoner jump into a cart, and take something out from a box which was covered with a sack, and which since proves to be three papers of halfpence; he dropped one paper in getting down; I saw the halfpence on the prisoner at the Justice's; I believe them to be the same.</p>
